    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "880\nJETS\nConvair 880 jets, years ahead for years to come... now on\nNORTHEAST AIRLINES",
      "MOST\nCOMPLETE\nJET\nSERVICE\nALONG THE\nEAST\nCOAST\nMONTREAL\nBOSTON\nNEW YORK\nPHILADELPHIA\nBALTIMORE\nWASHINGTON\nJACKSONVILLE\nTAMPA\nST PETERSBURG\n-CLEARWATER\nFORT LAUDERDALE\nMIAMI\nNORTHEAST WELCOMES AMERICAN EXPRESS, CARTE\nBLANCHE, DINERS' CLUB OR AIR TRAVEL CARDS\nNORTHEAST\nAIRLINES\nThis majestic 880 jet fleet\nwould be meaningless if the\nservice and schedules were\nnot geared to the needs of\nthe jet-age traveler. Signif-\nicantly, Northeast provides\nthe most complete jet serv-\nice along the East Coast —\nfrom Montreal to Miami.\nOf course every 880 jet car-\nries airfreight, so in addi-\ntion to regular vacation and\nbusiness travel, many firms\nthat depend on fast distri-\nbution take advantage of\nNortheast's frequent sched-\nules for shipping their prod-\nucts by air. Northeast has\nalso installed new and mod-\nern reservations, communi-\ncations, ticket offices and\nbaggage handling facilities\nto meet the exacting re-\nquirements of the jet age.\nThe next time you plan a\ntrip call your Travel Agent\nor Northeast Airlines. Fly\nthe jet that is years ahead\nfor years to come ... the\nNortheast Convair 880 jet.\n2008."
    ],
